    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "STANDARD FORM NO. 64",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Office Mem [unclear]um • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "TO : DIRECTOR, FBI DATE: March 31, 1950",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, NEW ORLEANS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Special Agent [REDACTED] of the New Orleans Division, has a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "brother, [REDACTED] of the [REDACTED] advertising agency,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "[REDACTED], Denver, Colorado. [REDACTED] has advised",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Special Agent [REDACTED] that an employee of the [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "[REDACTED] has been contacted by one [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "street, telephone [REDACTED], Denver, Colorado, regarding Flying Discs.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "[REDACTED] is alleged to have told [REDACTED] in January, 1950, that he",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "[REDACTED], knows a prominent Denver oilman named [REDACTED], also known",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "as a \"Mysterious Mr. X\", and an official of the [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "[REDACTED], Denver, Colorado. [REDACTED] is claiming that he leased land in",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "the Mojave Desert in California and that on this land a flying disc had",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "been found intact, with eighteen three-foot tall human-like occupants,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "all dead on it but not burned. Further, that the disc was alleged to be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "of very hard metal and near-indestructible. [REDACTED] is said to have",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "exhibited a radio set to [REDACTED] purported to be a souvenir of the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "space-disc.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "According to [REDACTED] has been telling of this story off and",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "on for the three month period prior to January, 1950, and is said to have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "notified [REDACTED] of it weeks prior to the publication of a flying disc",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "article published in the True Magazine, and one by FRANK SCULLY published",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "in the Variety Magazine in January, 1950. [REDACTED] said to have been",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "visited by DONALD KEHOE, author of the article in the True Magazine.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Further data was furnished that [REDACTED] had been telling the tale so",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "prolifically in Denver that he claimed to have had telephone calls from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "Washington, D. C. and from the Federal Bureau of Investigation in which he",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "was requested to keep the information to himself and that, thereafter,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "he became mysterious about the entire matter.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "It is noted that considerable publicity regarding these discs has been",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "found in Denver and other papers.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "This information is being furnished the Bureau and the designated offices",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "for informational purposes.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
